    weeklyCampaignPreflightAssetReadinessCopy: `Rise With The Tribe Weekly Campaign Preflight Asset Readiness Kit:\n\nCampaign entering preflight: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.name}\nWeek: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.week} (${weeklyCampaignPrompt.label})\nHashtag: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.hashtag}\nCampaign member reach: ${campaignPerformanceSummary.memberReach || 0}\nActive campaign challenges: ${campaignPerformanceSummary.active || 0}\nReferral joins: ${referralJoins}\nPending feature submissions: ${featureReviewQueue.length}\n\nManual preflight asset readiness checklist:\n[ ] Compare the copy freeze, readiness decision, preflight owner handoff, approved launch angle, consent-cleared proof references, support-risk note, and Feature Me queue before asset prep starts.\n[ ] Confirm launch-card headline, caption input, Story/Reel hook, hashtag, app-first CTA, consent-safe proof reference, and support-routing note are ready for human design or copy work.\n[ ] Keep every asset app-first: challenge join, first log, referral invite, Feature Me with consent, support route, or free-loop fallback only.\n[ ] Record asset owner, reviewedAt timestamp, approved asset inputs, evidence reference, open support risk, and preflight asset handoff before any human creates final launch-card, caption, Story, Reel, or carousel assets.\n\nThis is a manual Weekly Campaign Preflight Asset Readiness Kit only. Do not auto-post to Instagram, schedule posts from the app, scrape posts, scrape comments, scrape DMs, store inbound replies, store Instagram identities, create attribution records, count link opens, add tracking pixels, export per-user activity, share private responses, share user content without consent, share unreviewed submissions, write referral state, grant rewards, create purchases, write entitlements, unlock paid access, imply paid access is live, promise outcomes, imply medical results, offer discounts, promise refunds, auto-message users, or pressure members.`,
    weeklyCampaignPreflightLaunchPacketQaCopy: `Rise With The Tribe Weekly Campaign Preflight Launch Packet QA Kit:\n\nCampaign entering preflight: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.name}\nWeek: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.week} (${weeklyCampaignPrompt.label})\nHashtag: ${weeklyCampaignPrompt.hashtag}\nCampaign member reach: ${campaignPerformanceSummary.memberReach || 0}\nActive campaign challenges: ${campaignPerformanceSummary.active || 0}\nReferral joins: ${referralJoins}\nPending feature submissions: ${featureReviewQueue.length}\n\nManual preflight launch packet QA checklist:\n[ ] Compare the asset readiness note, copy freeze, readiness decision, owner handoff, approved launch angle, consent-safe proof references, support-risk note, and Feature Me queue before packet QA starts.\n[ ] Confirm the packet has one approved launch-card headline, caption input, Story/Reel hook, hashtag, app-first CTA, manual DM/comment reply boundary, consent proof reference, support-routing note, and preflight owner.\n[ ] Keep the packet app-first: challenge join, first log, referral invite, Feature Me with consent, support route, or free-loop fallback only.\n[ ] Record packet QA owner, reviewedAt timestamp, approved packet inputs, evidence reference, open support risk, and final preflight handoff before any human opens the campaign preflight checklist.\n\nThis is a manual Weekly Campaign Preflight Launch Packet QA Kit only. Do not auto-post to Instagram, schedule posts from the app, scrape posts, scrape comments, scrape DMs, store inbound replies, store Instagram identities, create attribution records, count link opens, add tracking pixels, export per-user activity, share private responses, share user content without consent, share unreviewed submissions, write referral state, grant rewards, create purchases, write entitlements, unlock paid access, imply paid access is live, promise outcomes, imply medical results, offer discounts, promise refunds, auto-message users, or pressure members.`,
